   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>The max size is, theoretically, 10MB. That's what the nginx configuration says.

I made a custom HTTP 413 page, and I claimed the max size is 4MB, since I tested
with a 4.5MB photo, and it worked fine.

Testing the custom HTTP 413 error page now, by uploading a 11MB "photo".</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
 
